      "comment_id" : 83697963,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Thanks! I used this for sum BigDecimal numbers: BigDecimal sum = in.getItems().stream().map(it -&gt; (it.getValue() != null) ? it.getValue() : BigDecimal.ZERO).reduce(BigDecimal.ZERO, BigDecimal::add);"
