    "body" : "<p>You can use reduce method:</p>\n\n<pre><code>long sum = result.stream().map(e -&gt; e.getCreditAmount()).reduce(0L, (x, y) -&gt; x + y);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>long sum = result.stream().map(e -&gt; e.getCreditAmount()).reduce(0L, Integer::sum);\n</code></pre>\n"
