    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use collect method to add list of integers.</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Integer&gt; list = Arrays.asList(2, 4, 5, 6);\nint sum = list.stream().collect(Collectors.summingInt(Integer::intValue));\n</code></pre>\n"
