    "answer_id" : 52022173,
    "question_id" : 30125296,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use <code>reduce()</code> to sum a list of integers.</p>\n\n<pre><code>int sum = integers.values().stream().reduce(0, Integer::sum);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
