      "comment_id" : 102587035,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Unfortunately we don&#39;t have any int-array. So <code>IntStream.of()</code> won&#39;t work for this problem, unless we&#39;re making something spooky like this: <code>IntStream.of( integers.values().stream().mapToInt( Integer::intValue ).toArray() ).sum();</code>"
